name: Roomit
supportRelayerBy: Roomit is a Limited Liability Company (LLC), officially registered as PT Roomit Trimiko Digital. Established in Indonesia in 2022, Roomit is driven by a team of IT professionals dedicated to leveraging blockchain technology, with a primary focus on DePIN (Decentralized Physical Infrastructure) technology. Roomit specializes in developing a decentralized virtual private network (VPN) service and facilitating transaction validation across multiple blockchains. The primary mission of Roomit is to provide reliable infrastructure and offer secure, private, and decentralized transaction services.
